FOR THE JUICE.

208
00:11:10,334 --> 00:11:13,801
SO I JUST FIGURED, MAYBE,
IF YOU GO IN MY PLACE THIS YEAR

209
00:11:13,834 --> 00:11:15,567
AND YOU'RE NOT
A COMPLETE BONEHEAD

210
00:11:15,601 --> 00:11:18,235
IN THE ROMANCE DEPARTMENT,
THEN MAYBE YOU'VE GOT A SHOT.

211
00:11:18,267 --> 00:11:20,034
