FOR THE TWO OF YOU,

219
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:45,267
BUT MAYBE THERE'S SOME HOPE
FOR ME, TOO.

220
00:11:45,300 --> 00:11:47,367
WHAT YOU THINK, SKILLS?

221
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:49,100
